10. a6 {I could easily see a human doing this. After10...Qb611.Nc3!White wins a pawn. Black is not without compensation, but I don't think it will be enough to equalize.} 
11. Nc6
11. Qe8
12. Ba3 {Suprisingly, Black is immediately losing material, and is totally lost.} 
