13. Ne5 {The best move in a bad position.13...Nc714.f4±Black is strategically busted with e4-e5 on the way. None of his pieces can move.} 
14. f4
14. Nf7
15. Nxf7
15. Rxf7 {This is even worse than15...Bd4+, as we will see in the next line.} 
