15. Nxc5
15. Nxc5
16. dxc5
16. Bxc5 {Now, it looks like Black is equalizing - next he castles, and what could go wrong? But one more accurate move seals his fate.} 
17. Qc3 {Absolutely devastating. Black will need to tuck his bishop all the way back to f8 to avoid losing his whole kingside.} 
17. Bf8
18. Be3 {White should easily win the game with his active rooks coming to the d and c-files before Black can complete his development. The bishop having to go back to f8 was a real punch to the gut.} 
