14. cxd5 {Black is arguing that our rook coming to d1 was something of a wasted tempo, and he is claiming that once he castles and starts bringing rooks to the c-file, he should be able to trade a bunch of stuff and be basically fine. There is no doubt, this position is pretty thin for White, but I don't think Black can claim full equality just yet.14...exd5?!Black will regret trying to get creative.15.e4!White is blowing up the center and Black has to be precise not to lose right away.} 
