9. O-O {The rook is immune from capture, and otherwise with Nbd2 and Rab1 coming next, Black will not be able to keep the position under control.} 
9. Qxa1 {9...Be710.Nbd2Ra1-b1 is coming next, and Black is about to collapse.} 
10. Bd4 {White wins the queen, and the game.} 
